subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Arinze Onuaku scored a career-high 23 points and pulled down 12 rebounds, Donte’ Greene added 22 points, and host Syracuse held off St. John’s, 76-70, in the Big East opener for both teams.
